 The resident, who lives in Agra street, was startled out of his sleep when he heard a loud bang only to realise that an armed man was standing over him.
At this point, five other armed men came into the room with his family members. As the armed men tied up his family, one of the assailants started assaulting him. The robbers ransacked their home and made off with an undisclosed amount of cash and six cell phones.
